freeglut v3.8.0 for MS VisualStudio

This package contains libs and DLLs for MS VisualStudio (VC++).
Please check out https://www.songho.ca/opengl/gl_freeglut.html for details.

32-bit
======
Compile Search DIR: .\freeglut\include
Link Search DIR   : .\freeglut\lib
Link Option       : /D FREEGLUT_STATIC

64-bit
======
Compile Search DIR: .\freeglut\include
Link Search DIR   : .\freeglut\lib\x64
Link Option       : /D FREEGLUT_STATIC
